     5 | 0x0020  | RSET
     6 | 0x0040  | SEND
     7 | 0x0080  | SOML
     8 | 0x0100  | SAML
     9 | 0x0200  | VRFY
    10 | 0x0400  | EXPN
    11 | 0x0800  | HELP
    12 | 0x1000  | NOOP
